show.description: When a devoted sister returns from abroad to attend her brother’s surprise wedding, she becomes the victim of brutal jealousy and a shocking betrayal that leads to a tragic miscarriage. Now, with her family's honor at stake, a storm of revenge, revelations, and corporate power games erupts—threatening to destroy everything.
